# Build / generated output
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.turbo/

# Lock files
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# Database migrations (read only when task is about migrations)
**/migrations/

# Static assets
**/assets/images/
**/assets/fonts/
**/public/images/
**/public/fonts/

# Environment / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pem

# IDE / OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Test snapshots
**/__snapshots__/

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log
